    "body": "Turns out, Go http requests add `Accept-Encoding: gzip` automatically (and do the decoding). And if the header is set manually then it wouldn't auto decode. See also #383 \r\n\r\nAlso merged #380 with minor cleanup\r\n\r\n* Current release candidate: [v1.4.0-rc4](https://github.com/flashbots/mev-boost/tree/v1.4.0-rc4)\r\n* Docker image: [flashbots/mev-boost:1.4.0-rc4](https://hub.docker.com/layers/flashbots/mev-boost/1.4.0-rc4/images/sha256-1491d0be77309615c7c43f1b1f9418f84ab36b587c448ab5cce4b56c2e5f5d15?context=explore)",
